{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2137750/extras/intro.png?t=1734811786\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Frameland delivers a retro experience with charming pixel art and an original 16-bit soundtrack. Timed turn-based battles keep you on the edge of your seat. Explore a rich world and uncover Condorra\u2019s dark past.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2137750/extras/heading_explore.png?t=1734811786\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2137750/extras/gif_explore.gif?t=1734811786\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The world of Condorra is full of secrets waiting for you to discover! Your loyal robot companion Proto can dig, grapple, and blast through obstacles, revealing mysteries others can\u2019t reach. Or take to the skies with your airship to revisit familiar locations or explore uncharted territories!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2137750/extras/heading_combat.png?t=1734811786\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2137750/extras/gif_battle.gif?t=1734811786\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Combat isn\u2019t just about hitting hard\u2014it\u2019s about hitting at the right time. Time your moves to perfection, exploit weaknesses, and manage your resources to outsmart your enemies. Customize your characters with powerful remnants to turn the tide of battle and deliver crushing blows.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2137750/extras/heading_interact.png?t=1734811786\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2137750/extras/gif_interact.gif?t=1734811786\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Immerse yourself in a world where everything is interactive\u2014every NPC has something to say, and nearly every object holds a story. It\u2019s an RPG with the curiosity-driven charm of a point-and-click adventure, full of hidden surprises and new discoveries.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2137750/extras/heading_story.png?t=1734811786\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2137750/extras/gif_story.gif?t=1734811786\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Experience a gripping tale told from two perspectives\u2014twists and turns included. Thrown into the cold, machine-ravaged world of Condorra, Ryiu must navigate deadly threats, form uneasy alliances, and uncover the world\u2019s darkest secrets. But the road ahead is fraught with danger, and every truth comes at a cost\u2014what will it take for Ryiu to get home?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2137750/extras/heading_more.gif?t=1734811786\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">All action, no filler with 8\u201315 hours of playtime</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Lovingly hand-crafted pixel art</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Original 16-bit soundtrack with 60+ tracks</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Lots of minigames</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Late-game sidequests</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">No random encounters</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Pet dogs\u00a0\ud83d\udc36</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"City of the Sunset","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2137750/e0d2bd73c6049029d261e26fe74e938613367914.jpg"},{"name":"Daylight at Last","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2137750/e6d59a2822e88bcb20fd05241214d1ac223916f7.jpg"},{"name":"Journey into the Unknown","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2137750/57b5e131f6b989a19ba162fa6c3c2d350b3310ac.jpg"},{"name":"On Distant Shores","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2137750/f57da1c777806138383d3a5540b61c5579e8610c.jpg"},{"name":"An Empire Crumbles","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2137750/9752e63e7e400834d97e414ce9d747d63383f3a8.jpg"},{"name":"Reunited","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2137750/0ce4ed97c36e87c800b3d0b00c5079dd20c560a3.jpg"},{"name":"A Binary Tale, Told","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2137750/0e72a068261ad4614c7ed8c80d51a5880a590c3d.jpg"},{"name":"The Right Rhythm","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2137750/7dab8e973926ec6eaa0a125c2407ce19d070976a.jpg"},{"name":"Trader at Heart","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2137750/9ca4fa2b7451ac0df17a630498b08dc3de622df5.jpg"},{"name":"Protector of the Innocent","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2137750/20a9b901d5c21fe647d76cf25bdd931c41081058.jpg"}],"total":32},"background":"htt